TITLE: Kalki Avatar | Grp Member Suman Lata Divine Experience With Maa Adi Parashakti Noor Ananta Ji
VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dEN6Mz7MudU
LANGUAGE: Hindi (auto-translated)

SUMMARY:
Suman Lata describes her spiritual journey that began in 2018, intensifying during the COVID period when she focused more on meditation. Despite limited time due to household responsibilities, she gradually progressed. Many spiritual guides came into her life, but everything changed when she heard Maa Baba speak during Kumbh 2025. She watched their videos on YouTube and Facebook, and recognized that a genuine energy was working through Maa-Baba -- one that reveals absolute truth without any sugar-coating.

What impressed her most was Maa's direct, unvarnished communication style. She mentally prayed to meet Maa at either Kumbh or Kashi Vishwanath, but when that wasn't possible, Maa seemingly heard her inner call and the WhatsApp group link appeared. Since joining, her energy level transformed dramatically. She started noticing angel numbers (repeating number patterns) that she had been seeing but couldn't understand before. Maa taught her to decode messages from the universe -- that nothing is a coincidence, every event carries a meaning. She describes how a light has entered her life, bringing good vibrations and a feeling of being on the right path. She prays for Maa's continued guidance and for attaining self-realization (aatma-gyan).

KEY REVELATIONS:
- Spiritual journey since 2018, intensified during COVID with meditation
- Impressed by Maa's direct, truth-telling communication style without any sugar-coating
- Angel numbers she'd been seeing for years finally made sense after joining the group
- Learned to decode universe's messages -- nothing is a coincidence, everything carries meaning
- Experienced a dramatic shift in energy level and awareness (jagrukta) after joining

YUG PARIVARTAN ASPECT: Energy Activation

